"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-970x644.webp 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-300x199.webp 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-768x510.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-1536x1019.webp 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-2048x1359.webp 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-750x498.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-1140x756.webp 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-465x310.webp 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-620x413.webp 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/03/MAAP_AEON_PR-Selects_4x3__41-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption>MAAP</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve been impressed with the comfort and hot weather performance of the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/gear-of-the-year-2023-clothing\">Maap Alt_Road jersey</a> featuring it in our Gear of the Year in 2023, as well as the brand’s <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/maap-womens-team-bib-evo-shorts-review\">Team Evo bib shorts</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Maap prices the short sleeve Aeon jersey at £170 / $230 / €185 and the long sleeve at £190 / $260 / €210.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can buy online from Maap, via Maap retailers and from its LaB stores in Melbourne, Amsterdam, Berlin, Seoul, Singapore, Hong Kong and Taipei. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Find out more and buy now at <a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/road\" target=\"_blank\">maap.cc</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/newsletters\"><img width=\"970\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-970x351.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-970x351.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-300x109.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-768x278.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-1536x556.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-2048x741.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-750x271.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-1140x412.jpg 1140w\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/maap-aeon-kit\">Maap’s new Aeon kit is made for longer rides</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Pnorman","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"2711946baea9ca301c99a9dfcf1812b2184f15df7219f6b48476e0ddf3e5d949","category":"Cycling"}